" Most likely.",
" My reply is no.",

" Outlook not so good.",
" Outlook good.",
" Reply hazy, try again.",
" Signs point to yes.",
" Very doubtful.",
" Without a doubt.",
" Yes.",
" Yes – definitely.",
" You may rely on it."
];
var item = choices[Math.floor(Math.random() * choices.length)];
var message = "🎱" + item
Actions.storeValue(message, 1, "MessageVar", cache);
